<p>Doughnut 2 has now released for public consumption. I have fixed some browser compatibility issues. Also, there are now 2 variations of Doughnut, ‘Glazed’ and ‘with Sprinkles’. Glazed is a simple pre-compiled version of Doughnut it has pre-named columns. The with Sprinkles version provides an improved (and reduced) codebase but requires a Sass compiler to build out the styles.</p>
